Human-first Raspberry Pi diagnostics

Usage: pi-doctor [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  check           Run the full diagnostic probe set
  explain         Explain a Raspberry Pi diagnostic topic
  support-bundle  Create a support bundle with reports and raw captures
  doctor          Run a focused diagnostic doctor
  completions     Generate shell completions
  help            Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json
      --quiet
      --verbose
      --no-color
      --timeout <SECONDS>  [default: 3]
  -h, --help               Print help
  -V, --version            Print version
